# Repo debugging notes

Before debugging or redeploying in **this repo**, read `.cursor/rules/debugging.md` if it exists.

- **Failed experiments** — do not retry listed approaches.
- **Current working approach** — prefer documented patterns.
- After a failed fix attempt, **append** a bullet under Failed experiments (date + symptom + what not to repeat).

Deploy success in the log is not enough for dryl.io apps — run `node ../directory/scripts/verify-dryl-app.mjs` when applicable (see directory `.cursor/rules/deploy-verify-loop.mdc`).
